<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
<div style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
<p style="color: #e45206; font-size: 32px; line-height: 36px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 25px; text-align: left; font-weight: bold;">{{lead.First Name:default=Friend}},</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">I wanted to let you know that we have extended our exclusive offers <span class="appleLinksGray">to July 15!</span> This is the best package of deals I&rsquo;ve ever seen since I&rsquo;ve been with Direct Energy Solar. And they won&rsquo;t be around for much longer, so you must act today.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Can I plan on reviewing the details with you so I can show you how much additional savings we can add to your proposed system? Let me know when you might be available for a follow up. In the meantime, here are the details of the promotion:</p>
</div>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="634" align="center" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
