<tr>
<td style="background-color: #fdf1eb; border-bottom: 5px solid #ffffff;" colspan="2">
<p style="text-align: center; color: #1c3f94; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px;"><strong>Get $1,500<sup>1</sup> When You Choose to Go Solar With Us!</strong></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">At Direct Energy Solar, we like to help homeowners save. That&rsquo;s why we would like to offer you a $1,500 discount when you sign your contract with us <span class="appleLinksGray">by July 15, 2015</span>. It&rsquo;s more money to put back into your pocket for better use than electricity bills, and it&rsquo;s our best cash-back offer yet!</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="background-color: #fdf1eb; border-bottom: 5px solid #ffffff;" colspan="2">
<p style="text-align: center; color: #1c3f94; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px;"><strong>We Guarantee Your Installation or You Get $500!<sup>2</sup></strong></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">We want to get you on the road to electricity savings as quickly as possible. If you sign with us <span class="appleLinksGray">by July 15, 2015</span> and we do not install your solar system within 75 days, you will receive a $500 rebate or deduction from the final invoice.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom: 5px solid #ffffff;" colspan="2"><img src="http://pages.directenergysolar.com/rs/astrumsolarinc/images/RowOfCustomers.jpg" border="0" alt="Direct Energy Solar Customers" width="634" height="134" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="background-color: #fdf1eb; border-bottom: 5px solid #ffffff;" colspan="2">
<p style="text-align: center; color: #1c3f94; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px;"><strong>Just for Meeting with Us, You&rsquo;ll Get a Free<sup>3</sup> 6-month Heating &amp; Cooling Repair Essentials Plan from Direct Energy!</strong></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">There&rsquo;s no obligation to buy when you agree to meet with us to review your potential energy savings. In fact, we&rsquo;re offering you an instant bonus just for letting us show you how much solar may save you on your monthly energy bill.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">Meet with a Direct Energy Solar consultant for an in-home consultation <span>by July 15, 2015</span> and receive a free 6-month Heating &amp; Cooling Repair Essentials Plan from Direct Energy Protection Plans. This plan provides worry-free coverage for inconvenient repairs.</p>
<p style="text-align: center; color: #1c3f94; font-size: 21px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px;"><strong>Your 6-month Plan Includes:</strong></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px; text-align: center;">No service visit charge, no deductibles, no age restrictions</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px; text-align: center;">$500 coverage per repair incident up to $2,000 annually</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px; text-align: center;">24/7 emergency service</p>
</td>
