<p style="color: #1c3f94; font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;">Contact me to discuss the numbers with you or any other questions you have about going solar with Direct Energy Solar.</p>
